{"tid":2058641,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台建「兩棲船塢運輸艦」衞太平島","createTime":"2020-06-10T10:20:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T10:20:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"19b52592c5350179d12eae8deacea69c87db0cb5","tid":2058641,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:20:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200610/A2M6ZYE2SXG6VQ7J3FG6MGENFU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200610%2FA2M6ZYE2SXG6VQ7J3FG6MGENFU%2F&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa2a%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=ee42a620\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200610%2FA2M6ZYE2SXG6VQ7J3FG6MGENFU%2F&h=227e12b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200610/A2M6ZYE2SXG6VQ7J3FG6MGENFU/</a><br />\n<br />\n台建「兩棲船塢運輸艦」衞太平島<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DQNZAJ7YNOEUMWPEFRXJQVKYYY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDQNZAJ7YNOEUMWPEFRXJQVKYYY.jpg&h=69fba371&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣海軍司令劉志斌(左)昨出席安放龍骨典禮。<br />\n<br />\n中美關係緊張帶動南海局勢不穩，台軍制訂南沙太平島「衞疆計劃」，其中海軍新興建的「新型兩棲船塢運輸艦」，昨日在高雄廠區舉行安放龍骨典禮，該艦造價46.35億新台幣（約12億港元），將於2022年交付後服役，執行捍衞海疆的任務，這亦是台灣「國艦國造」的指標型項目之一。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美F-18戰機曾降台南 京強烈抗議<br />\n<br />\n（已節錄）"}]}